tools.description:
Retrieve the play count and last played time for a specific track.

Args:
    track_id (str): The unique ID of the track.

Returns:
    dict:
        On success:
            {
                "success": True,
                "data": {
                    "play_count": int,
                    "last_played_at": str  # ISO 8601 datetime
                }
            }
        On failure:
            {
                "success": False,
                "error": "Track not found"
            }

Constraints:
    - The track_id must exist in the library.
